@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_aevlhs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(0.91)
    tmp = (v2 / (wp.sin(v0 + 0.27) * (v0 + 0.25 * v1 + 0.72)))
    v2 = wp.abs(0.34)
    tmp = 0.83
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v0 + 0.75 - tmp + 0.46)))
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
